metadata.name: such great heights
metadata.description:
do you remember last night? the emotion, the vibe – the endless streets of this city; our city. sweat-soaked shoulders touching in the dark haze of the club; our friends lining up at the bar, glowing faces staring at phones. or was it fireworks on the roof? i’m losing track now. i remember walking by the east river, backlit by the neon sky. new york nights are limitless and so are we. never forget these nights. 
*nightscenes NYC*
